local.taxAnswer:
Ku mushahara mbumbe wa buri kwezi ungana na {{gross}}, igipimo cy'ibikurwaho ni:
PAYE: {{paye}}
Pansiyo y'umukozi: {{pension}}
Umusanzu w'ikiruhuko cyo kubyara: {{maternity}}
CBHI: {{cbhi}}
Umushahara usigara: {{net}}
Imisanzu y'umukoresha: {{employer}}
Amafaranga yo guteganya kohereza buri kwezi: {{remittance}}

Ibi bishingiye ku byiciro bya PAYE n'imisanzu ikoreshwa mu Rwanda. Emeza ibidasanzwe nk'inyungu zitari amafaranga, akazi ka kabiri, ubusonerwe, cyangwa ubwishingizi bwihariye mbere yo gutanga imenyekanisha.

